parameters:
It's unfortunate about my husband... but I can't stay down
forever. I have to take care of the children who lost their
parents. Those children also need support, after all...

My child... is causing a disturbance, but... I'm
unexpectedly excited... I hope it's not causing any trouble?

\SE[8]It's not a bother at all... I've only been helped by
Tita.

Well, if that's the case, then it's fine... But really, who
does she take after...

My child said, I'm going to marry Lunaroa-sama! It's
troubling, you know, even though they're still a child...

\SE[2]Ah, I didn't give Laura a flower decoration, did I?
\SE[3]If it's okay, do you have one?

\SE[15]Oh my...\.You two are so close. \!\SE[15]It's
really heartwarming...
\SE[14] (How can you see it that way...)

\SE[12]I want to become stronger. \SE[13]Really... enough to
protect everyone.

\SE[12]If I can be of use... Take me with you. \SE[13]I want
to become stronger, even if just a little.
Show me the results of your training
\SE[14]I'll show you that I can be useful...!
\SE[59]Hey...! How dare you act so high and mighty, Laura!

\SE[12]What I'm lacking right now is a special move, I
guess. \!\SE[43]First, I need to think of a name....

\SE[2]Hmm... I have some free time until it's time to go
out. Maybe I should tease and play with Ryan... \SE[48]

\SE[14]Laura! Take me with you! \SE[10]I have to show the
big sister something good! That's why!
I want to see a good place!
I've already seen a good place!

\SE[18]I can be useful, right...?! \.You know that very
well!
Rebecca has been added to the party!!
\SE[14]Why?! I don't care if you regret it later!

\SE[56]I wonder if what I'm lacking right now is a special
move...? \!\SE[18]I need to come up with a good name for it.

\SE[99]Hmm... I have no idea at all. \SE[17]Melissa is
amazing...

Ronoa seems to be full of motivation. Shall we take her with
us?
I won't take her with me
Ronoa has been added to the party!!

\SE[4]Oh, Aua! \SE[1]Hey, Choua, Chichinane. Aaah,
Chichanji. Ania, Chichotoemoa?

\SE[70]Giri... Do you understand? \!\SE[30]No, but I can't
be certain...

\SE[47]Lunaroa... Will you ever be able to speak someday?
\!\SE[38]If it's impossible...
\SE[1]Well, if I can be with you forever, then it's fine!

\SE[15]Ah, you feel like you need my help? \SE[15]Well...
I guess there's no helping it.

\SE[16]Hehe~ Well then, shall we get excited and give it our
all?
Melissa has been added to the party!!

\SE[14]Eh? I wanted to show you the results of my
training...

\SE[2] Oh, Laura. You look beautiful today. Your skin is
glowing. \SE[45] Did something good happen, by any chance?
\SE[35]Please stop with the technical sexual harassment....

\SE[2]There are many things I've lost... but... \SE[45]It's
not just sad things, right? There were also wonderful
things... Don't you think so?

Melissa seems to like coffee. She's mature and composed...
that's the impression I get.

It's a familiar fountain pen... Maybe it's a memento from my
grandmother.
There is a cactus. ... Lunaroa also likes... The cactus...?

It's a flower that Ronoa-chan picked. It's arranged so
beautifully, it's terrifying... She might have a talent for
that kind of thing.

This is Ryan's training sword. You can feel the dedication
from the wear and tear...

Rebecca's whip. The well-worn leather fits snugly in the
owner's hand, while the tip of the fall inflicts a pain that
clings to the victim's body.

It's just an ordinary clock. Time cannot be turned back, but
children are moving forward. I can't afford to lose either.

Books on 'swordsmanship' and 'military strategy' are densely
lined up. Ryan's earnestness is clearly evident...

...Oh? Behind the large books, there seems to be a hidden
door...?

\SE[11]Instead of hiding it sneakily, \.you should just
openly reveal it too!! \!\SE[29]\SM[pop]Your embarrassing
fetish...!!
\SE[29]I'm telling you, this isn't my hobby...!!
Nikita has a bra. No... it's big. Too big.

Beautiful robes are displayed. I wonder if she admires this
kind of magician...? ...Huh?

Beautiful robes are displayed. It seems like there's nothing
else here anymore...
Melissa's clothes are inside. Well, of course they are.

I shouldn't be doing something like this...! But... I can't
stop my hands...!
It seems that 'panties' are no longer available...
Huh...? There's something placed under the bed...
I have to pretend I didn't see this...
